commitResults.messageTitle: Add Appointment class and related classes
commitResults.messageBody:
1. Implement Appointment
2. Implement AppointmentDateTime (dd-MM-yyyy HHmm, dd-MM-yyyy)
3. Implement AppointmentLength (length must be positive integer)
4. Implement AppointmentLocation (no invalid symbols)
5. Implement AppointmentType (no constraints)
6. Implement AppointmentNote (no constraints)
7. Implement AppointmentStatus (4 statuses)

Add ParserUtil methods and tweaked appointment-related classes such that
empty input leads to empty strings being created in the classes.

LinkAppointmentCommandParser and ParserUtil uses the empty strings
instead of creating objects with empty string parameters.

Add Name field (clientName) to Appointment class for ease of comparing
appointments in UniqueAppointmentList.

Create AppointmentNotFoundException and DuplicateAppointmentException in
order to follow how UniquePersonList was implemented.
